# secscan-mcp

Python MCP server: orchestrate security scanners, normalize findings for agents.

- Design: [PLAN.md](../../PLAN.md)
- Package: `src/secscan_mcp/`
- Agent guide: [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md)

## Build order

1. `normalize.py` — Finding schema, severity, dedupe, secret redaction
2. `engines/*` — one adapter per scanner CLI
3. `runner.py` — parallel runs, timeouts, path safety
4. `server.py` — MCP tools (`scan_secrets`, `scan_code`, `scan_all`, etc.)
5. `tests/` — fixtures + integration markers

## Quality gate

Before marking work done: `make check` (ruff + mypy + pytest).
